{"tid":993670,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"我做左3間公司嘅基因檢測","createTime":"2019-01-24T06:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T03:34:44.000Z","uid":119102,"like":11,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"11270ad12aa0302d613ac3d287145a7dc943099a","tid":993670,"uid":119102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T06:04:37.000Z","msg":"首先見到大陸就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果D 可以唔洗睇<br />\n3間大陸 基因檢測公司<br />\nWegene 微基因  (W)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wegene.com/shop/?_source=R_442365_2B21D9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wegene.com%2Fshop%2F%3F_source%3DR_442365_2B21D9&d=7jr721pX1FVco0rX7P5j%2BACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=f3a2e138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wegene.com/shop/?_source=R_442365_2B21D9</a><br />\n23魔方 (23)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.23mofang.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.23mofang.com%2F&d=7jr721pX1FVco0rX7P5j%2BACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=ada0d7f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.23mofang.com/</a><br />\n水母基因 (水)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.somur.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.somur.com%2F&d=7jr721pX1FVco0rX7P5j%2BACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=22660953\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.somur.com/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DapUbQO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDapUbQO.jpg&h=b3eb6e42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DbzkRQQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDbzkRQQ.jpg&h=9fc82bd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n配件差唔多，都有口水收集管、說明書、(得WEGENE有密封袋)。口水管原理一樣，就是吐口水到果條填充線，俾D保存液同口水撈埋。但口水管(23 同水)係一樣通過旋轉漏鬥使收集的口水下流至保存液，而w的口水保存液存在於漏鬥蓋內，在收集完口水後按個漏斗蓋壓一下，咭穿薄膜後保存液流出於同口水撈埋。wegene係操作上唔會咁易出現失誤。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4gfwd76.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4gfwd76.png&h=2851761c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3 個都係用APP 睇報告, 得(W) 可以微信係睇 同轉做PDF睇<br />\n<br />\n你唔洗諗係香港寄番大陸, 冇一間做<br />\n我出深圳寄用順豐到付, (23 同水) 有係順豐登記,快遞單可以唔填都得<br />\n(W) 就冇係順豐登記, 要填返,快遞單<br />\n<br />\nWegene 微基因 深圳<br />\n23魔方 成都<br />\n水母基因 北京<br />\n<br />\n最快係W,  跟住23, 最後水母 確認收到我D口水<br />\n出報告時間同上, W 好快5日就有, 23就 7日,水母 12日<br />\n<br />\n1) 祖源成份<br />\na, Wegene 微基因<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Try2kU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTry2kU3.jpg&h=62d4df09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4wihUe4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4wihUe4.jpg&h=37e1f02f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vUsuLmK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvUsuLmK.jpg&h=d24a3a9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uzcFR1L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuzcFR1L.jpg&h=20714b40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qjsbee5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQjsbee5.jpg&h=6c6d0870&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cdbfF1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcdbfF1Q.jpg&h=24225020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ye08gAa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fye08gAa.jpg&h=6248a5a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nb, 23魔方<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  100% 中華民族<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VMt53k4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVMt53k4.jpg&h=52d2e336&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cmhnk7K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcmhnk7K.jpg&h=d7818fe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gc9pzsL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbn